Depends on what you're looking for in a "comfy" relationship story. Here are a few of my favorites. Note: many of these are also on FA or Weasyl, but I like SoFurry's filtering system the best.

>Fur and Skin series (OneDirtyDog)
https://www.sofurry.com/view/980957
Multi-part human/wolfess story. Has fantasy elements, and is a good read if you have the time.

>Alpha Bitch (capthavoc123)
https://www.sofurry.com/view/643513
German shepherd bullies protagonist in a school setting, but eventually warms up to him. Might not be what you'd consider a "comfy" relationship, but it ends happily all the same.

>Among the Wolves (Baron03)
https://www.sofurry.com/view/554042
Human is adopted by a tribe of wolves and raised as one of their own. Most of this guy's stuff is pretty good.

>Fate also smiles (Wirewolf)
https://www.sofurry.com/view/251
A human gets a reclusive new vixen neighbor to open up. It's definitely a long one, but there's a reason it's one of the top most popular stories on the site

>Love is a Number (K-I-K)
https://www.sofurry.com/view/62277
Another human/vixen story similar to the one above, though arguably a little more dramatic at times.

I'm partial to canine stories, so there's a little bias here. But like I said, most sites have a filtering system if you're looking for other types of anthros.
